title: The Woodsy Association - A Tiny Owl Knits Pattern Collection
description:
Join The Woodsy Association and the raucous little band of woodland animals that will gather around you for cuddles! This sweet assortment of wrist-ees from tiny owl knits designer Stephanie Dosen brings together an adorable cast of critters that includes a Badger, Owl, Deer, Wolf, and Racoon. This whimsically delightful collection includes the instructions for the wrist-ees along with charted instructions for your new furry friends. Worked from the top-down, the wrist-ees are worked flat using stranded instarsia or you can choose to adorn your wrist-ees with the animals by using duplicate stitch afterwards. Each of the five wrist-ees are finished off with The Woodsy Association charms - the cute little feathers, tails, paws, and antlers that dangle at the wrist. Wear them in the forest with pride and The Woodsy Association will know you are a friend to the animals!

The wrist-ees in The Woodsy Association collection are sized for s-xl (3, 3.25, 3.5, 3.75" wide).
